  "texts": [
    "Let P → B be the principal (ρ(π 1 (B)) δ ⋉ N)-bundle to which M is associated.",
    "Since (ρ(π 1 (B)) ⋉ N)/ρ(π 1 (B)) ≃ N is contractibleby assumption, there is a reduction of the structure group of P to ρ(π 1 (B)) δ [KN63, Ch.",
    "I, Prop. 5.6 & Thm.",
    "Consider a bundle atlas for P associated to a cover {U i } of B, with locally constant transition functions taking values in ρ(π 1 (B)).",
    "As M is the associated bundle, a bundle atlas for it is given by {U i × N}, with the same transition functions."
